      <div class="thumb-headline thumb-headline-bottom">
        <div class="thumb-h">STP is three stages in order, and the chapter returns to a named stage in every section.</div>
        <p class="body-text">Segment the market. Target the slice you can win. Position the brand in the mind of the buyers you chose.</p>
