      <div class="thumb-headline thumb-headline-bottom">
        <div class="thumb-h">Four standard bases answer four different questions about the buyer, and the working segmentations combine two or three.</div>
        <p class="body-text">Geographic asks where. Demographic asks who. Psychographic asks what the buyer values. Behavioral asks what the buyer does.</p>
        <p class="source">Kotler et al. (2022); Smith, Journal of Marketing (1956).</p>
