        <div class="thumb-h">STP picks the category the brand competes in. The penetration laws govern growth once that choice is locked.</div>
        <p class="body-text">Toyota's launch of Lexus was the STP move. Growing Lexus afterward was a penetration question. Two laws, two jobs.</p>
        <p class="source">Sharp (2010); Kotler et al. (2022); Toyota Lexus launch case.</p>
